data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ActiveWriterDomainModel.Description
data.value: A Visual Studio 2005 addin to design domain models and to generate code decorated with ActiveRecord attributes based on the model.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/UseNullables.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to generate code using nullables where possible.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/CaseOfPrivateFields.Description
data.value: Tells ActiveWriter how to name private fields of properties if the Access of Property is PropertyAccess.Property (Default)

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/GenerateMonoRailProject.Description
data.value: Tells ActiveWriter to generate a seperate MonoRail project with View and Controller code, taking this file's output as the model.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/MonoRailProjectName.Description
data.value: Name of the MonoRail project. If a project with the same name already exists in the solution, it won't be added to the solution.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/UseGenerics.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to generate code using generic collections where possible. This setting is overridable in class level.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/UseBaseClass.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to generate classes inherited from a base class. If Base Class Name property is empty, ActiveRecordBase or ActiveRecordBase<T> will be used depending on the Use generics property.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/BaseClassName.Description
data.value: Defins the base class to be inherited. Does have no effect if Use Base Class property is set to false.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/GeneratesDoubleDerived.Description
data.value: If true, will generate a base class with all functionality and a derived partial class to support customization through overrides.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/DoubleDerivedNameSuffix.Description
data.value: Suffix appended to base class names in double derived code generation. Defaults to "Base", if not supplied.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/UseGeneratedCodeAttribute.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to decorate each class with GeneratedCodeAttribute. Some tools evaluate existance of this attribute to handle code differently.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/Target.Description
data.value: Defines the experimental code generation target.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/AssemblyPath.Description
data.value: Provides assembly load path for Castle.ActiveRecord.dll and related assemblies. If required assemblies are in GAC, this setting is omitted. If not and is this setting is blank an error will be thrown during code generation.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/ActiveRecordAssemblyName.Description
data.value: Provides assembly name to be used during code generation.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/NHibernateAssemblyName.Description
data.value: Provides assembly name to be used during code generation.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/RelateWithActiwFile.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to add hbm.xml file as a nested file of this .actiw file. Otherwise, file will be added as a standalone item to the project.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/UseVirtualProperties.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to generate virtual properties where possible.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/Namespace.Description
data.value: The namespace to be used in generated code. If not supplied (default), ActiveWriter will use the namespace from the native project structure.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/AdditionalImports.Description
data.value: List of additional imports to be added to the generated class.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.Model/ImplementINotifyPropertyChanged.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to implement INotifyPropertyChanged interface in each class generated. This setting is overridable in class level.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/DiscriminatorColumn.Description
data.value: Discriminator column for a table inheritance modeling

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/DiscriminatorType.Description
data.value: Column type (like string or integer) for the discriminator column

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/DiscriminatorValue.Description
data.value: Value that represents the target class on the discriminator column

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/Lazy.Description
data.value: Enable lazy loading for the type

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/Proxy.Description
data.value: Associates a proxy type with the target type

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/Schema.Description
data.value: Schema name associated with the type

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/Table.Description
data.value: Table name associated with the type

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/DynamicInsert.Description
data.value: Specifies that INSERT SQL should be generated at runtime and contains only the columns whose values are not null.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/DynamicUpdate.Description
data.value: Specifies that UPDATE SQL should be generated at runtime and contains only those columns whose values have changed.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/SelectBeforeUpdate.Description
data.value: Specifies that NHibernate should never perform an SQL UPDATE unless it is certain that an object is actually modified. In certain cases (actually, only when a transient object has been associated with a new session using update()), this means that NHibernate will perform an extra SQL SELECT to determine if an UPDATE is actually required.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/Polymorphism.Description
data.value: Determines whether implicit or explicit query polymorphism is used.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/Mutable.Description
data.value: Specifies that instances of the class are (not) mutable.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/BatchSize.Description
data.value: Specify a "batch size" for fetching instances of this class by identifier.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/UseAutoImport.Description
data.value: The auto-import attribute lets us use unqualified class names in the query language, by default. The assembly and namespace attributes specify the assembly where persistent classes are located and the namespace they are declared in.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/BaseClassName.Description
data.value: If set and if model level base class usage is set, overrides any base class defined in the model.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/UseGenerics.Description
data.value: If set (other than Inherit), overrides model level generics generation for this class.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelClass/ImplementINotifyPropertyChanged.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to implement INotifyPropertyChanged interface in this class.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty.Description
data.value: A property or field of a class

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/KeyType.Description
data.value: Denotes if the property is a normal property, a key or part of of a primary key.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/SequenceName.Description
data.value: Name of the sequence to be used for the primary key. Required when Generator is Sequence.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/CompositeKeyName.Description
data.value: Name of the composite key class to be generated.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/DebuggerDisplay.Description
data.value: Decorates the class this property belongs to with DebuggerDisplay attribute, using this property as the display source. Example: [DebuggerDisplay("Name = {Name}")]

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/Validator.Description
data.value: Defines validators to be used on the property.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/UniqueKey.Description
data.value: A unique-key attribute can be used to group columns in a single unit key constraint.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/Index.Description
data.value: Specifies the name of a (multi-column) index.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.ModelProperty/Check.Description
data.value: Create an SQL check constraint on either column or table.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.NamedElement/Description.Description
data.value: Description of the element. This will appear in a <summary> Xml comment.

data.name: Altinoren.ActiveWriter.NestedClass/ImplementINotifyPropertyChanged.Description
data.value: Instructs ActiveWriter to implement INotifyPropertyChanged interface in this class.
